    An implementation of the model object 'Line2 T'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Line R
    • Compond R
    • Control Mode
    • Operation Mode
    • Meter End
    • Control Side
    • Power Demand
    • Power Demand2
    • Scheduled DC Voltage
    • Rectifier
    • Inverter
    • Rectifier2
    • Inverter2
